messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Please pray that I overcome sexual idolatry and masturbation.

Heavenly Father, we come before you seeking strength and guidance to overcome the struggles of sexual idolatry and masturbation. We ask for your forgiveness and cleansing from all unrighteousness. We renounce these sins and ask for your help in breaking all curses and strongholds associated with them. We present our bodies to you as a living sacrifice, and we pray for the fire of God to burn out all unclean lust from our lives. We also ask for the breaking of ungodly soul ties with former lovers and partners. In the name of Jesus Christ, we command all spirits of lust and perversion to leave us. We earnestly seek you, Lord, and ask for your strength and freedom. Amen.
